As a user I want to have a clean UI
As a user I want the application to be intuitive
As a user I want multiple options for my queries
As a user I want the full information of the recipes on one simple to read page
As a user I want navagation on the site to be easy
As a return user I want past searches to be available
As a return user I want recommandations for new recipes based on my past searches
As a return user I want popular searches to be available for new ideas
As a administrator I want to see a clear list of users
As a administrator I want users to have a way to give feedback
